description:
Bravo has gifted us with FOUR (!!!) new Housewives episodes this week! Comedian Angelina Spicer stops by to recap the premiere of #RHOA. Danny also recaps the new #RHOC, touches on #RHOD, shares his DMX theorem, and gives a lil Southern Charm scoop.


#RHOC- 8:30ish

#RHOA/Angelina- 23:52ish
